'''Thermal detonator tape''' was used to explosively breach sealed doors. Utilizing a basic adhesive blended with [[Detonite/Legends|detonite]] gel, it could break through most sealed hatches. On the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Geonosis/Legends|Geonosis]] during the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|first battle]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the [[Clone commando/Legends|Republic commando]] nicknamed [[Darman Skirata|Darman]] used thermal tape to attach a thermal detonator to a triple-sealed [[Blast door/Legends|blast door]]. The door needed to be breached so [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta Squad]] could pass through, but dirt covering the alloy made it difficult for the tape to take hold, causing a delay.

